The standard agreed upon procs per minute (PPM) rate is 2 in main hand, and 1 in offhand (Also 2 if using a 2h weapon).  This is based on a 305 Dex and no Weapon Affinity (WA) or Combat Effects. Note PPM is not affected by haste.<br>
<br>
So, if yer using a 150 DD in main, it adds 5 DPS (150 x 2 / 60) and 2.5 DPS offhand (150 x 1 / 60).  <br>
<br>
And, each level of WA is about 9% increase in procs (well, WA5 is 45%, but concrete logs were not taken at WA1, 2, 3, 4...).   Put another way, with WA5, yer 150DD is adding about 7.3 DPS main and 3.6 offhand.  <br>
<br>
